<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Setup Wizard - Felton Brushes</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body class="setup-page">
  <div class="setup-wizard">
    <h1>Felton Brushes Attendance System Setup</h1>
    <p>Let's set up your attendance tracking system. This wizard will guide you through adding work stations and employees.</p>

    <div class="setup-stats">
      <div class="stat-box">
        <div class="stat-number"><%= stationCount %></div>
        <div class="stat-label">Work Stations</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-box">
        <div class="stat-number"><%= employeeCount %></div>
        <div class="stat-label">Employees</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="setup-actions">
      <a href="/admin/manage" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">
        <% if (employeeCount > 0) { %>
          Continue to Management
        <% } else { %>
          Start Setup
        <% } %>
      </a>

      <% if (employeeCount > 0) { %>
        <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-secondary">Go to Dashboard</a>
      <% } %>
    </div>

    <div class="setup-help">
      <h3>Setup Steps:</h3>
      <ol>
        <li>Create work stations (Lines and stations)</li>
        <li>Add employees (manually or bulk import)</li>
        <li>Assign employees to stations</li>
        <li>Configure Twilio and Vapi (see documentation)</li>
      </ol>

      <p>You can add stations and employees from the <strong>Management</strong> page.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
